Log in to the Azure Portal and navigate to the Azure AI Services or Azure OpenAI resource that is powering firstProject / KbChatBot.

On the left-hand menu, click on Access control (IAM).

Click the + Add button at the top, then select Add role assignment.

Search for and select the Cognitive Services OpenAI User role (or the broader Cognitive Services User role if the bot uses multiple AI services). Click Next.

Under "Assign access to", choose User, group, or service principal.

Click + Select members and search for the specific identity (App Registration, Service Principal, or User) that generated the API key you provided to me.

Click Review + assign to save the changes.
